rComments: Just save your life and don't take any courses with her, do anything or leave the country.

Firstly, the most important part is that I couldn't understand anything she says. Secondly, there was too much context at the same time, and you are not able to memorize and understand it. Finally, don't take this course with her NEVER save your GPA and nerves, just drop it or leave the country.

Lectures are prerecorded "for foreign students". I respect wanting to ensure international students are treated fairly but it would be better for both foreign and local students if the lectures were live + recorded so we all can benefit from real time questions. She is bland and seems generally uncaring. I cannot believe she's a university prof.

I physically cannot understand the words Dr. Chen speaks. It makes it so hard to learn anything. She is basically a robot. Her TA's are her saving grace. SOOOO much content at once. Legit no live class so if u need help you are at the mercy of emails or office hours. Midterms and Final only. Lockdown browser and webcam. No prof to switch to sucks.
